      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for a daily driver. The exterior has some visible wear, including several minor scratches and a small dent on the passenger side door. Inside, the upholstery shows some fading and signs of use, but all major components are functional. It has been regularly maintained, though it may require some minor cosmetic attention to truly shine.",
